body_html: I also can compile tf master with bazel 0.12. However, I'm still befuddled that the same tf commit (from branch 1.7) failed to compile after a suite of package updates. That doesn't necessarily mean it wasn't a tf issue in 1.7, just that it wasn't manifest until after a separate update (which I don't think changed bazel).
